Nelson Ascencio https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nelson_Ascencio 0 Nelson Ascencio (born August 30, 1964) is a Cuban-American actor and comedian. Ascencio is most notable for his membership in the recurring cast of comedians on sketch comedy series MADtv and for playing Flavius in The Hunger Games film series.
